item.title: Oops! These Are The Most Awkward 'Walk Of Shame' Photos We've Ever Seen
item.description: sickchirpse Everyone likes to party now and then to let off some steam and get crazy with friends. What you have to remember when you’re partying, however, is how you’re planning to get home the next day! Not everyone knows exactly where they’ll end up the night of a party, and the next day, they’re forced to do the Walk of Shame. From the heels they’re still wearing to the messy hair, you can tell these ladies got down with their bad selves last night, and who knows what kind of trouble they got into.
